  "body": "### Description\r\nAs a node operator, I want to be able to set the DNS Discovery URL via CLI so that I can use DNS Discovery URLs for networks other than the pre-configured named mainnet networks. \r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n* DNS discovery URL is set via command line flag, such as `--discovery-dns` and the node uses it.  For a stand alone test a manually configured testnet should be used instead of the `--network` flag and DNS discovery URL is echoed in the info log\r\n",
